s (especially old-time Actresses) who have starred in [[Bollywood]] films as leading roles. the aim of this article to provide the information for their fan who doesn't know her original name due to change their original(birth) name to screen name and people know them by the screen name. Many old-time actresses were belonging to the Royal Family ancestor. Their Royal beauty makes them different from other actresses. As like [[Parveen_Babi#External_links|Parveeb Babi]]   [[Sultana_(actress)|Sultana]]  [[Zubeida]][[https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fatma_Begum|Fatma Begum  ]]   [[https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Naseem_Banu|Naseem Banu]][[Nimmi ]][[https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sara_Ali_Khan|Sara Ali Khan Pataudi]]\n\n==1920s==\n<!-- When adding column entries, remember to update the rowspan count. -->\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n! Year with<br>lead role\n! Name \n! Debut as<br>lead role\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"|1922\n|[[Fatma Begum]]\n|Veer Abhimanyu\n|-\n|[[Sultana (actress)|Sultana]]\n|Veer Abhimanyu\n|-\n|1923\n|[[Zubeida]]\n|Kohinoor\n|-\n|1926\n|[[Gohar Mamajiwala]]\n|Baap Kamai\n|-\n|}\n\n==1930s==\n<!-- When adding column entries, remember to update the rowspan count. -->\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n! Year with<br>lead role\n! Name \n! Debut as<br>lead role\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |1930\n|-\n|[[Mehtab (actress)|Mehtab]]\n|Kamaal-e-Shamsheer \n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" |1931\n|[[Esther Victoria Abraham]]\n|Toofani Tiruni\n|-\n|[[Kajjanbai]]\n|[[Shirin Farhad (1931 film)|Shirin Farhad]]\n|-\n|[[Khursheed Bano]]\n|Eye for an eye\n|-\n| rowspan=\"1\" |1932\n|[[Firoza Begum (actress)|Firoza Begum]]\n|Bewafa Qatil\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |1933\n|[[Sardar Akhtar]]\n|Id Ka Chand\n|-\n|[[Bibbo (actress)|Bibbo]]\n|Rangila Rajput\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |1935\n|[[Jaddanbai]]\n|[[Talashe Haq]]\n|-\n|[[Naseem Banu]]\n|[[Khoon Ka Khoon]]\n|-\n|1939\n|[[Begum Khurshid Mirza]]\n|Bhakti\n|-\n|}\n==1940s==\n<!-- When adding column entries, remember to update the rowspan count. -->\n{| class=